description:
With this DLC you'll unlock: 

- your own dog that follows you everywhere! 
- active bonus that increases the amount of cash you collect from fish
- secret fish you can feed to earn beauty cup points
- new fishbowl decoration
- 100 gems

Have fun with your new pet, take care of your new fish, decorate the aquarium, spend your gems on various upgrades and enjoy the bonus!
name: Aquarium Land: Puppy
